---
title: Forbidden Rice Salad with Sugar Snap Peas, Beets & Mango
description: Forbidden rice may have earned it's name from ancient China, where only emperors could enjoy this rare, nutrient-dense grain. Luckily, you don't have to be a royal to enjoy it today. Tossed with juicy mango, crisp snap peas, and sweet beets, this salad is full of unexpected flavors. The cilantro-lime vinaigrette pulls them all together!
